The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Kallis may lead vs India 

OUR SPECIAL CORRESPONDENT

Bangalore: Jacques Kallis is expected to captain South Africa during the forthcoming three-match ODI series against India in Ireland. 

According to The Telegraphs sources, regular captain Graeme Smith still needs time to recover from knee surgery. 

One understands senior pro Shaun Pollock, too, wont be there and the South African selectors could use the matches to assess some youngsters. 




